### ðŸ“¡ Screencast Button

This folder contains additional CSS tweaks for the screencast button.

1. Go to your Jellyfin **Admin Dashboard** in your web browser
2. Navigate to **Dashboard â†’ General â†’ Custom JavaScript**
3. Paste the following code:
```js
const castObserver = new MutationObserver(function() {
    const castBtn = document.querySelector('.headerCastButton');
    if (castBtn) {
        castBtn.style.setProperty('display', 'flex', 'important');
    }
});
castObserver.observe(document.body, { childList: true, subtree: true, attributes: true });
```

4. Click **Save** and hard refresh your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)
